                    <span>This little book has a lot of wisdom. Sometimes it's a bit hard to grasp at first but it's nothing a little zazen wont fix. It's well worth the read if you're interested in Chan especially from the Rinzai sect as Huang Po was Lin-chi's (Rinzai)teacher.</span>
                  
              
